@startuml
start

:Select Application;
note right
User selects an existing job application.
end note

:Choose New Status;
note right
User chooses a new status such as Interviewing or Rejected.
end note

:Update Status;
note right
System updates the application status.
end note

:Save Changes;
note right
Updated status is saved.
end note

:Show Update Confirmation;
note right
System shows confirmation of the update.
end note

stop
@enduml